{"type":"message","id":"29bb4b75","parentId":"d7edf947","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:22:19.741Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering workspace backup and skills**\n\nI'm thinking about performing a daily backup of my workspace. I might want to focus on self-improvement later, perhaps in the afternoon or evening. For now, it seems like I need to look over some checklists related to workspace backup and quantitative operations. I wonder if this involves more than one skill, but it feels more like just a single task that I need to inspect further. Let's check those checklists!","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_rgzWJfGJekMVbWHVNGpvWI9G","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-workspace-backup.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_YrS9PVkStzwauCTWLixMCX8U","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/heartbeat-quant-ops.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"gmn","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773879723858}}
{"type":"message","id":"27852b2a","parentId":"29bb4b75","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:22:19.798Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_rgzWJfGJekMVbWHVNGpvWI9G","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Workspace Backup\n\n## Trigger\n- 每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 是否有未提交修改\n\n## Pre-flight\n- [ ] 进入 `~/.openclaw`\n- [ ] 运行 `git status`\n- [ ] 确认不包含敏感信息（credentials / tokens / secrets）\n\n## Execution\n- [ ] 按修改类型分组提交：\n  - skill / config / workspace / docs / chore\n- [ ] 执行 `git add -A`\n- [ ] 执行 `git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"`\n- [ ] 执行 `git push`\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] 推送成功\n- [ ] 如有需要，记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n## Notes\n- 敏感信息不要提交\n- 优先保证重要工作区修改已同步\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773879739796}}
{"type":"message","id":"ebe0a0c5","parentId":"27852b2a","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:22:19.799Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_YrS9PVkStzwauCTWLixMCX8U","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Quant Ops\n\n## 08:50 Morning News Push Check\n\n### State File\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查 `status` / `generated_at` / `last_success_at` / `last_failure_at`\n- [ ] 若交易日 08:50 之后仍无当日成功记录，主动汇报阻断原因\n- [ ] 若 `status` 为 `GENERATION_FAILED` 或 `PUSH_FAILED`，主动汇报错误摘要与日志路径\n- [ ] 若已成功且无新增变化，保持安静\n\n## Quant Research Mainline Health\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.json`\n- 终端摘要：`🩺 量化投研主链巡检：OK/WARN/ALERT`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查退出码与 `overall_status`\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报晨报 / 稳定策略 / 回测队列是哪一项断裂\n- [ ] `WARN`：汇报缺口文件或未生成入口\n- [ ] `OK` 且无新增变化：保持安静\n\n## Trading-day Premarket Precheck (09:20-09:40)\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 无需用户提醒，交易日自动执行\n- [ ] 当日已执行过则跳过\n- [ ] 非交易日保持安静\n- [ ] 失败时主动汇报阻断原因与报告路径\n- [ ] 成功时汇报 `precheck` / `orders` / `brief` 路径\n\n## Daily Strategy Audit\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_strategy_audit.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] `PASS`：简要汇报核心指标与路径\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报未通过项与修复建议\n\n## Daily Enhancements\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_enhancements.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json`\n- `research/reports/daily_enhancement_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 双源验证失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 热力图失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 正常运行：简要汇报上涨/下跌板块数\n\n## Live Dashboard + Feishu Push\n\n### Commands\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_YYYYMMDD.html`\n\n### Push Rules\n- [ ] 成功后主动发飞书 DM：面板路径、precheck 状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要\n- [ ] `needs_permission=true`：提示给 OpenClaw/终端 Full Disk Access\n- [ ] 导出为空：提示“同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空”\n- [ ] 生成失败：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\n- [ ] 非交易时段不含“可执行买价”，只给预算/优先级/开盘触发条件\n- [ ] 当天已推送且无新增数据，可保持安静\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773879739798}}
{"type":"message","id":"05293320","parentId":"ebe0a0c5","timestamp":"2026-03-19T00:22:35.522Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Processing heartbeat tasks**\n\nI need to respond to a heartbeat poll according to the rules. First, I should scan for applicable skills. If only one skill fits, I’ll read its SKILL.md. This task revolves around heartbeat processing, but it doesn't seem obvious which applies.\n\nI also need to check if any scheduled work is due since quiet hours ended at 8:00 AM. The morning news push isn't due yet, but a health check might be. If nothing is urgent, I can simply reply with HEARTBEAT_OK.**Executing daily checks**\n\nI need to conduct daily checks for scheduled work since it's currently 8:22 AM. I should perform a workspace backup check and a quant ops daily check. I only need to report proactively if there are new files, reports, or script results. \n\nHowever, running these checks might create new files, which complicates things since the heartbeat rules state I should only report three types of updates. If something needs attention, it might be better to report that rather than simply replying HEARTBEAT_OK.**Determining scheduled work execution**\n\nI need to figure out if any scheduled work should run, and if so, whether the outputs show no changes, which would mean I can stay quiet. However, if running a script creates a report file today, that counts as a \"new file/report landed,\" and I should report it. This could lead to every heartbeat prompting a report, which complicates things. \n\nLet me also check if quant ops and workspace backups were completed today, and see how the state files look. The morning news push isn't due yet, and the premarket precheck isn't until 9:20.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ELwJbTnGz0aB6CLIoTxCgpLj","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"git -C /Users/ling/.openclaw status --short","workdir":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace