{"type":"message","id":"cd828336","parentId":"e01de94d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:40:33.882Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_KNS1rFuv908F2FmBI4Hr7wxC","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Status: done\nPriority: P0\nStarted: 2026-03-19\nUpdated: 2026-03-19 22:51\nWorkspace: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace\nOwner: main-session\n\n## Goal\n量化系统 P0/P1 漏洞清单 + 自动检验补强计划\n\n## Acceptance\n- ✅ 个股实时前置门禁并入下午自动重跑主链（stock_level_realtime_gate_v2.py）\n- ✅ 错误买入自动纠偏/回滚第一版（apply_paper_rollback.py）\n- ✅ 下午自动重跑强制刷新链具备机器可检验能力（run_intraday_risk_recheck.py）\n- ✅ 多源实时宽度兜底（intraday_market_breadth.py，三源：AkShare→eFinance→Tushare）\n- ✅ 写账户前 Python 深层阻断（prewrite_paper_guard.py v2）\n- ✅ THS/TDX 统一路由接入主链（DataFetcherManager + 三源降级兜底）\n\n## Current\n- P0/P1 全部完成，所有 Acceptance 满足\n\n## Next\n\n## Completed\n- [2026-03-19] daily_stock_analysis 三层融合（layer 1/2/3）\n- [2026-03-19] 三个模拟盘全部平仓撤销（commit 5abdadf）\n- [2026-03-19] 热力图/CTO/透镜面板刷新（commit d1755ef）\n- [2026-03-19] prewrite_paper_guard v2（commit 79068b3）\n- [2026-03-19] THS/TDX 统一路由接入主链（commit d499de8, 8743e3b, 083b938）\n- [2026-03-19] 三源降级兜底验证通过\n\n## Evidence\n- d499de8 feat: stock_level_realtime_gate_v2 use DataFetcherManager (THS→Pytdx→Efinance→腾讯降级)\n- 8743e3b feat: intraday_market_gate use DataFetcherManager (THS→Pytdx→Efinance→腾讯降级)\n- 083b938 feat: intraday_market_breadth add Tushare as 3rd fallback (AkShare→eFinance→Tushare)\n- 79068b3 feat: prewrite_paper_guard v2 deep block\n- 5abdadf fix: rollback all 3 paper trading profiles\n- d1755ef feat: refresh heatmap/CTO/lens panels with real sector data\n- ca0801b/0b4e668/b8627fc daily_stock_analysis 3-layer integration\n\n## Real Source Verification (2026-03-19 22:51)\n| 脚本 | 实际数据源 | 验证结果 |\n|---|---|---|\n| stock_level_realtime_gate_v2 | tencent_fallback | 002920: ¥113.75, -1.47% ✅ |\n| intraday_market_gate | tencent_direct | 上证-1.39%, 深证-2.02% ✅ |\n| intraday_market_breadth | tushare.daily | 472涨/4499跌, 9.5% ✅ |\n\n## Blockers\n- THS/Pytdx 在 macOS 环境无 SDK 且网络不通（Windows 有 SDK 时自动以最高优先级工作）\n\n## Rules\n- 只有在 Acceptance 全部满足时才设置 Status: done。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773938433880}}
{"type":"message","id":"8bcfbf9d","parentId":"cd828336","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:40:33.884Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_sD1FEvR8FLFASef8nXRlj0eU","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Workspace Backup\n\n## Trigger\n- 每天检查一次 `~/.openclaw` 是否有未提交修改\n\n## Pre-flight\n- [ ] 进入 `~/.openclaw`\n- [ ] 运行 `git status`\n- [ ] 确认不包含敏感信息（credentials / tokens / secrets）\n\n## Execution\n- [ ] 按修改类型分组提交：\n  - skill / config / workspace / docs / chore\n- [ ] 执行 `git add -A`\n- [ ] 执行 `git commit -m \"[类型] 更新描述\"`\n- [ ] 执行 `git push`\n\n## Verification\n- [ ] 推送成功\n- [ ] 如有需要，记录到 `memory/heartbeat-backup-log.md`\n\n## Notes\n- 敏感信息不要提交\n- 优先保证重要工作区修改已同步\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773938433883}}
{"type":"message","id":"cc24158f","parentId":"8bcfbf9d","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:40:33.885Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_X7u90RwTEo4Kwk2qPNHiOoD3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Quant Ops\n\n## 08:50 Morning News Push Check\n\n### State File\n```bash\ncat ~/.openclaw/workspace/memory/global_market_morning_0850_state.json\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查 `status` / `generated_at` / `last_success_at` / `last_failure_at`\n- [ ] 若交易日 08:50 之后仍无当日成功记录，主动汇报阻断原因\n- [ ] 若 `status` 为 `GENERATION_FAILED` 或 `PUSH_FAILED`，主动汇报错误摘要与日志路径\n- [ ] 若已成功且无新增变化，保持安静\n\n## Quant Research Mainline Health\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 scripts/run_investment_research_mainline_guard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/investment_research_mainline_health_YYYYMMDD.json`\n- 终端摘要：`🩺 量化投研主链巡检：OK/WARN/ALERT`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 检查退出码与 `overall_status`\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报晨报 / 稳定策略 / 回测队列是哪一项断裂\n- [ ] `WARN`：汇报缺口文件或未生成入口\n- [ ] `OK` 且无新增变化：保持安静\n\n## Trading-day Premarket Precheck (09:20-09:40)\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/auto_run_premarket_precheck.py --available-cash 1000000 --account-nav 930000\n```\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 无需用户提醒，交易日自动执行\n- [ ] 当日已执行过则跳过\n- [ ] 非交易日保持安静\n- [ ] 失败时主动汇报阻断原因与报告路径\n- [ ] 成功时汇报 `precheck` / `orders` / `brief` 路径\n\n## Daily Strategy Audit\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_strategy_audit.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `research/reports/daily_strategy_audit_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] `PASS`：简要汇报核心指标与路径\n- [ ] `ALERT`：主动汇报未通过项与修复建议\n\n## Daily Enhancements\n\n### Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/run_daily_enhancements.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/sector_heatmap_summary.json`\n- `research/reports/daily_enhancement_YYYYMMDD.json`\n\n### Rules\n- [ ] 双源验证失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 热力图失败：主动告警\n- [ ] 正常运行：简要汇报上涨/下跌板块数\n\n## Live Dashboard + Feishu Push\n\n### Commands\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_app_data.py\npython3 scripts/sync_ths_exports.py\npython3 scripts/generate_live_global_dashboard.py\n```\n\n### Output\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_latest.html`\n- `research/reports/live_global_dashboard_YYYYMMDD.html`\n\n### Push Rules\n- [ ] 成功后主动发飞书 DM：面板路径、precheck 状态、年化/回撤/夏普、买卖记录数、A股温度摘要\n- [ ] `needs_permission=true`：提示给 OpenClaw/终端 Full Disk Access\n- [ ] 导出为空：提示“同花顺暂无可用导出数据/账户为空”\n- [ ] 生成失败：主动发报错摘要与修复建议\n- [ ] 非交易时段不含“可执行买价”，只给预算/优先级/开盘触发条件\n- [ ] 当天已推送且无新增数据，可保持安静\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773938433884}}
{"type":"message","id":"1cea00e3","parentId":"cc24158f","timestamp":"2026-03-19T16:40:33.887Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e7wnQwqMtX64KmibbuBHpVD4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Checklist: Heartbeat Self-Improvement\n\n## Command\n```bash\ncd ~/.openclaw/workspace\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/generate_daily_report.py\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_promote_learnings.py --apply --threshold 2\npython3 skills/self-improving-agent/scripts/auto_extract_skill_drafts.py --threshold 2\n```\n\n## Output\n- `memory/self_improvement_daily_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_autopromote_YYYYMMDD.md`\n- `memory/self_improvement_skill_drafts_YYYYMMDD.md`\n\n## Rules\n- [ ] 汇总 `.learnings/LEARNINGS.md` / `ERRORS.md` / `FEATURE_REQUESTS.md`\n- [ ] 统计高优先级待处理项、状态分布、area 分布\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 自动提升到 `AGENTS.md / TOOLS.md / SOUL.md`\n- [ ] 对 `Recurrence-Count >= 2` 的 learning 生成 skill 草稿到 `skills/<name>/SKILL.md`\n- [ ] **只生成草稿，不自动安装**到 `~/.openclaw/skills/`\n- [ ] 无论有无提升项，都主动发飞书 DM 汇报摘要与三个输出文件路径\n- [ ] 若无提升项，明确写“今日无自动提升项”\n- [ ] 若无技能草稿，明确写“今日无技能草稿生成”\n- [ ] 若发生自动提升，汇报被提升条目、目标文件路径、写入是否成功\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773938433885}}
